    "description": {
      "content": "The ElevenLabs Speech to Text API provides state-of-the-art transcription capabilities, converting spoken audio into accurate text. It supports multiple audio formats and languages, enabling developers to build applications that require reliable audio transcription. The API supports both synchronous and asynchronous processing modes.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: ElevenLabs Support",
